### Finance Dashboard API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@analystToken = YOUR_ANALYST_TOKEN_HERE
@viewerToken = YOUR_VIEWER_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### AUTH ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### 1. Register - Validate Email/Phone
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "+911234567890"
}

### 2. Verify OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "test@example.com",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### 3. Complete Registration
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "+911234567890",
  "name": "Test User",
  "password": "Test@123"
}

### 4. Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "admin@wombto18.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 5. Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### DASHBOARD ENDPOINTS (All Roles)
### ============================================

### 7. Get Dashboard Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8. Get Recent Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/recent?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### ANALYTICS ENDPOINTS (Analyst & Admin)
### ============================================

### 9. Get Category Breakdown
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/by-category
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 10. Get Monthly Trends
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/trends?year=2024
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 11. Get Top Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/top-categories
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### RECORDS ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### 12. Get All Records (Analyst & Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/records?page=1&limit=10&type=INCOME
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13. Get Single Record
GET {{baseUrl}}/records/RECORD_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 14. Create Record (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/records
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Monthly Salary",
  "amount": 50000,
  "type": "INCOME",
  "category": "Salary",
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "notes": "January salary payment"
}

### 15. Update Record (Admin Only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/records/RECORD_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Salary",
  "amount": 55000
}

### 16. Delete Record (Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/records/RECORD_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### USER MANAGEMENT ENDPOINTS (Admin Only)
### ============================================

### 17. Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 18. Get User by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 19. Update User Role
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID_HERE/role
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "ANALYST"
}

### 20. Update User Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

### ============================================
### PROFILE ENDPOINTS (All Authenticated Users)
### ============================================

### 21. Get My Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 22. Update My Profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "phone": "+919999999999"
}

### ============================================
### PERFORMANCE TESTS
### ============================================

### 23. Test Dashboard Performance (All endpoints)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/by-category
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/trends
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/recent
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### ERROR HANDLING TESTS
### ============================================

### 24. Test Invalid Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "invalid@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 25. Test Unauthorized Access (No Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/records

### 26. Test Forbidden Access (Viewer accessing Admin endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}

### 27. Test Invalid Record Creation
POST {{baseUrl}}/records
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Invalid",
  "amount": -100,
  "type": "INVALID_TYPE"
}
